{"tid":2092453,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"「大時代」重臨　A股見4大牛市指標全中!!!","createTime":"2020-07-03T08:21:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T03:24:51.000Z","uid":66271,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7287f1004153cd7d18ecf5795508f0c5f3b93d5e","tid":2092453,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T08:21:34.000Z","msg":"中港股市氣氛升溫，上證指數升穿3000點關口，恒指也重上25000點。由中概股回歸及新經濟股帶起的升市，未有抖氣的迹象。有分析指，近日內地股市呈現出4大指標，顯示A股或現牛蹤。<br />\n<br />\n指標一：內地券商股終於起動，頗似「大時代」的前奏。<br />\n<br />\n指標二：北向滬深股通交投活躍。周四（2日）北向資金的買賣總額近1,500億元人民幣，創歷史新高，淨流入金額達171.2億元人民幣。<br />\n<br />\n指標三：A股成交大增，兩市成交額突破1萬億元人民幣。<br />\n<br />\n指標四：自6月以來，融資融券餘額大增，大市活躍度明顯升溫。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2078a1b00aa2509413f735894c1f6bd596d62985","tid":2092453,"uid":134415,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T08:23:20.000Z","msg":"乖乖地食草把啦 唔係食屎架喇"},{"pid":"f22b0f0832941a9e7de6c7704ee4f37c91399b08","tid":2092453,"uid":31907,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T08:42:24.000Z","msg":"預視支那超級通脹來臨"},{"pid":"30834b6243a679c6783b92442c6692001b12b3b1","tid":2092453,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T08:45:43.000Z","msg":"A股行穩致遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n證明國家強大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9278561e36e9b2e6c4a23487a3060015981e9e85","tid":2092453,"uid":62749,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T08:46:37.000Z","msg":"支那<br />\n牛市就越行越短<br />\n熊市就越行越長<br />\n唔夠韮菜割<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99b5d0d4f126f71770842bf016ccb6f0dcdaefbd","tid":2092453,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T08:48:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/asse